description.text:
CORPORATE RATE - Standard Double
Breakfast included, served in the hotel restaurant; 5 Check-in is at 2 PM and check-out is at noon;
Apartment with bedroom and bathroom of 19 m²; It is the smallest apartment in the Hotel, with an unobstructed view and rear facing; It has a TV, split air conditioning, minibar, work desk, electronic safe for laptop, electronic lock, hairdryer, Nespresso machine and TRIFOR security lock door; All have a double bed; It only accommodates a maximum of 2 people and does not accommodate a crib or extra bed.

